import React from 'react'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'
function About() {
    return (
        <>
    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
    <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Ultra Coder</Card.Title>
       
        <Card.Text>
            Hi I am Ultra Coder Papa MERN. I will help you learn MERN stack very easily. MERN is one of the fastest growing tech stacks used in the industry of web development. So, let's gooo!!!!!!
        </Card.Text>
        <Card.Link href="#">Card Link</Card.Link>
    </Card.Body>
    </Card>
        </>
    )
}

export default About
